  "description": "IRS Transcript Shows 971 – What It Means for tax professionals: what it means, what to check next, common pitfalls, and how to generate a client-ready report.",
  "content": "<section>\n        <h2 id=\"what-it-means\" class=\"section-heading\">What It Means</h2>\n        <p class=\"article-text\">This is written for tax professionals who need to answer a client question quickly and correctly, without turning the call into a code-reading session.</p>\n       </section>\n       <section>\n        <h2 id=\"what-to-check\" class=\"section-heading\">What to Check Next</h2>\n        <div class=\"card-glass card-hover p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-700\">\n        <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-slate-300 text-sm\">\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-purple-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"/></svg><span>Check for holds, notices, or freeze indicators near the event.</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-purple-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"/></svg><span>Compare dates (posted vs expected client timeline).</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-purple-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"/></svg><span>Confirm the transcript type and the year (people send the wrong thing).</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-purple-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"/></svg><span>Look for the next logical code in the sequence (pattern beats trivia).</span></li>\n        </ul>\n        </div>\n       </section>\n       <section>\n        <h2 id=\"common-pitfalls\" class=\"section-heading\">Common Pitfalls</h2>\n        <div class=\"card-glass p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-700\">\n         <h3 class=\"font-semibold text-white mb-3\">Common pitfalls</h3>\n         <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-slate-300 text-sm\">\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-rose-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v4m0 4h.01M10.29 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0Z\"/></svg><span>Giving a promise instead of a probability and next-step checklist.</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-rose-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v4m0 4h.01M10.29 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0Z\"/></svg><span>Missing the notice date that explains the delay or hold.</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-rose-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v4m0 4h.01M10.29 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0Z\"/></svg><span>Mixing up IRS tools (WMR, letters, transcript dates) without reconciling them.</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-rose-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v4m0 4h.01M10.29 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0Z\"/></svg><span>Treating a single code as the full answer.</span></li>\n         </ul>\n        </div>\n       </section>\n       <section>\n        <h2 id=\"cta-parser\" class=\"section-heading\">Send a Clean Explanation</h2>\n        <p class=\"article-text\">Your client wants a summary, not a transaction list. Generate a client-ready report that explains what happened and what to do next.</p>\n        <div class=\"mt-6\">\n         <a href=\"/#how-it-works\" class=\"btn-primary text-lg inline-flex items-center justify-center\">Parse Transcript Now</a>\n        </div>\n       </section>",
